==Useful info==

These guys are a pushover. They are generally found in a mini vault or vault that has a [[queen ant]], with her attendant [[worker ant]]s and [[soldier ant]]s.

==Tips and tricks==
They're harmless. To [[Makhleb]] and [[Vehumet]] worshipers, they may be of some help restoring your health and magic.

==History==
Ant larvae were removed in [[0.12]]

